NARRATOR_W1_L2_HARD=W1-L2 Also, if you lose all lives, [c_red][shake]you go all the way back to the beggining.
NARRATOR_W1_L3=W1-L3 To pass this level, you have to learn to jump properly!
NARRATOR_W1_L4=W1-L4 Hell yeah! That's right! Now try getting to the top!
NARRATOR_W1_L5=W1-L5 Wait, oh, sorry! These coins, well they are only for skipping hard levels. Feel free to use them!
NARRATOR_W1_L5_HARD=W1-L5 Wait, oh, sorry! These coins, well they are only for skipping hard levels. Feel free to\nuse them, oh sorry, [c_red][wheel]you can't, this is HARD MODE!
NARRATOR_W1_L6=W1-L6 Good, now watch out for those yellow blocks!
NARRATOR_W1_L6_COINS=W1-L6 And you managed to get a lot of them huh? Well congratulations...
NARRATOR_W1_L6_COINS2=[c_yellow]W1-L6 Interesting...
NARRATOR_W1_L7=W1-L7 Time for a huge jump!
NARRATOR_W1_L7_COINS=[c_yellow]W1-L7 So you are telling me that you played this game before?
NARRATOR_W1_L8=W1-L8 Ohhhh, what is this?
NARRATOR_W1_L8_COINS=W1-L8 Alright, I guess that you like [c_yellow]coins
NARRATOR_W1_L9=W1-L9 I guess you now know the main mechanic of this game.
NARRATOR_W1_L9_COINS=[c_yellow]Looks like you really really like coins.
NARRATOR_W1_L10=W1-L10 Just a long level.
NARRATOR_W1_L10_COINS=W1-L10 Anyway I'm gonna stop here. Good luck on your [wheel][c_yellow]Coins%[/] run, I guess.
NARRATOR_W1_L11=W1-L11 Sometimes, you have to think before you play the level.
NARRATOR_W1_L12=W1-L12 I call this [c_yellow]'A lot of yellows 1.0'.
NARRATOR_W1_L13=W1-L13 This is called a [c_aqua]'Climb Jump'[/] and it is quite tricky to succeed. Please have a few tries.
NARRATOR_W1_L14=W1-L14 Either you go the easy way, or THE HARD way...
NARRATOR_W1_L14_HARD=W1-L14 Either you go the easy way, or THE HARD way... wait, [c_red]there is no easy way!
NARRATOR_W1_L15=W1-L15 Wait, where is this green stuff coming from?
NARRATOR_W1_L16=W1-L16 What the hell? Have you seen those green stuff back then?
NARRATOR_W1_L17=W1-L17 WHAT? Are you telling me there are even MORE [c_lime]GREEN BLOCKS?
NARRATOR_W1_L18=W1-L18 EVEN MORE GREEN STUFF? Okay, also this level is hard.
NARRATOR_W1_L19=W1-L19 Wow? You did it? Well congrats you deserve a medal. You are getting better!
NARRATOR_W1_L20=W1-L20 Anyway there is this huge hotdog that you need to take care of. I am going to sleep. ZzzzzZzzzzz
