NARRATOR_W2_L2=W2-L2 I dunno how you were able to defeat that hotdog, but sure.
NARRATOR_W2_L3=W2-L3 Anyway, here is your first [c_red]REAL[/] challenge.
NARRATOR_W2_L4=W2-L4 Do you remember when I told you that you should think before you play?
NARRATOR_W2_L5=W2-L5 What is this [c_fuchsia]purple thing?
